{"title":"Build up your own Titanium Gravel Bike with the new Thomson Piedmont Frameset","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/06/14/build-up-your-own-titanium-gravel-bike-with-the-new-thomson-piedmont-frameset/","date":1623681294000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><p>Well over a year since we originally set eyes on it, Thomson have named and made available their titanium gravel frameset; the Piedmont. Named after the Piedmont plateau near the Appalachian Mountains, this titanium frame is built with a geometry that would serve gravel riders in the region well, with tire clearance up to 44c and a carbon fork.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/14093810/Thomson-Piedmont-Gravel-a-scaled-1.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/14093810/Thomson-Piedmont-Gravel-a-scaled-1.jpg?ezimgfmt=rs:484x323/rscb18/ng:webp/ngcb18\" alt=\"thomson piedmont ttanium gravel bike bikepacking\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/14093810/Thomson-Piedmont-Gravel-a-scaled-1.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb18 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/14093810/Thomson-Piedmont-Gravel-a-scaled-1-297x198.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb18 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/14093810/Thomson-Piedmont-Gravel-a-scaled-1-800x533.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb18 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/14093810/Thomson-Piedmont-Gravel-a-scaled-1-120x80.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb18 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/14093810/Thomson-Piedmont-Gravel-a-scaled-1-768x512.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb18 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/14093810/Thomson-Piedmont-Gravel-a-scaled-1-696x464.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb18 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/14093810/Thomson-Piedmont-Gravel-a-scaled-1-1068x712.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb18 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/14093810/Thomson-Piedmont-Gravel-a-scaled-1-630x420.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb18 630w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb18 src ng ngcb18 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/14093810/Thomson-Piedmont-Gravel-a-scaled-1.jpg?ezimgfmt=rs:484x323/rscb18/ng:webp/ngcb18\" ezoid=\"0.9827519817461863\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/14093810/Thomson-Piedmont-Gravel-a-scaled-1.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb18 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/14093810/Thomson-Piedmont-Gravel-a-scaled-1-297x198.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb18 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/14093810/Thomson-Piedmont-Gravel-a-scaled-1-800x533.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb18 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/14093810/Thomson-Piedmont-Gravel-a-scaled-1-120x80.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb18 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/14093810/Thomson-Piedmont-Gravel-a-scaled-1-768x512.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb18 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/14093810/Thomson-Piedmont-Gravel-a-scaled-1-696x464.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb18 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/14093810/Thomson-Piedmont-Gravel-a-scaled-1-1068x712.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb18 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/14093810/Thomson-Piedmont-Gravel-a-scaled-1-630x420.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb18 630w\"></a></p><p>As with the titanium <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2021/04/28/thomson-say-hey-to-titanium-hooch-hardtail-frame-w-customizable-cockpit-components/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Hooch Hardtail</a> mountain bike, the Piedmont Gravel bike is sold as a frameset only. For <span>$</span>3,295, you get the base level build kit with Thomson’s own elite series stem, seat post, clamp, alloy bar, and carbon fork. Though, many riders will want to take advantage of the exclusive discount Thomson are offering on their premium components with the sale of the frameset.</p><figure id=\"attachment_261807\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-261807\"><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/14093816/Thomson-Piedmont-gravel-bike-ti-frame-top-head-tube-junction.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/14093816/Thomson-Piedmont-gravel-bike-ti-frame-top-head-tube-junction.jpg\" alt=\"thomson piedmont headtube titanium frame tig welded\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/14093816/Thomson-Piedmont-gravel-bike-ti-frame-top-head-tube-junction.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/14093816/Thomson-Piedmont-gravel-bike-ti-frame-top-head-tube-junction-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/14093816/Thomson-Piedmont-gravel-bike-ti-frame-top-head-tube-junction-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.co