on-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/14093816/Thomson-Piedmont-gravel-bike-ti-frame-top-head-tube-junction-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/14093816/Thomson-Piedmont-gravel-bike-ti-frame-top-head-tube-junction-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/14093816/Thomson-Piedmont-gravel-bike-ti-frame-top-head-tube-junction-630x420.jpg 630w\"></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-261807\">The Piedmont titanium gravel frame gets a brushed finish with sandblasted logos and a custom head tube badge</figcaption></figure><p>The Thomson Piedmont is fabricated in Taiwan from 3al 2.5v aircraft grade titanium, serving up a 70° head tube and 74° seat tube angle. A tapered 1 1/8 to 1.5 internal head set supports Thomson’s 45mm rake carbon fork with a 395mm axle-to-crown measurement.</p><figure id=\"attachment_261810\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-261810\"><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/14093841/Thomson-Piedmont-gravel-ti-frame-rear-triangle-dropouts-brake-mount-1.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/14093841/Thomson-Piedmont-gravel-ti-frame-rear-triangle-dropouts-brake-mount-1.jpg\" alt=\"thomson piedmont titanium gravel bike 700c x 44c tire clearance\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/14093841/Thomson-Piedmont-gravel-ti-frame-rear-triangle-dropouts-brake-mount-1.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/14093841/Thomson-Piedmont-gravel-ti-frame-rear-triangle-dropouts-brake-mount-1-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.co