ube-bottle-bosses-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/14093853/Thomson-Piedmont-titanium-gravel-frame-downtube-bottle-bosses-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/14093853/Thomson-Piedmont-titanium-gravel-frame-downtube-bottle-bosses-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/14093853/Thomson-Piedmont-titanium-gravel-frame-downtube-bottle-bosses-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/14093853/Thomson-Piedmont-titanium-gravel-frame-downtube-bottle-bosses-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/14093853/Thomson-Piedmont-titanium-gravel-frame-downtube-bottle-bosses-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/14093853/Thomson-Piedmont-titanium-gravel-frame-downtube-bottle-bosses-630x420.jpg 630w\"></a></p><p>Like the <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2021/04/28/thomson-say-hey-to-titanium-hooch-hardtail-frame-w-customizable-cockpit-components/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Hooch MTB</a>, the Piedmont Gravel Bike runs internal cable routing through the front triangle, with the rear mech cable and rear brake hose guided externally along the chainstays. The front triangle can accommodate two full size water bottles within the downtube, with a spare set of bosses on the top tube providing purchase for a small pack or other accessories.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/14093847/Thomson-Piedmont-gravel-ti-frame-tig-welds-1.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/14093847/Thomson-Piedmont-gravel-ti-frame-tig-welds-